text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_TodayWonSmartnessContest {
	"This POKéMON won the BEAUTY CONTEST
	here before.

	Well, guess what? Today, I made it
	win a SMARTNESS CONTEST!

	My abilities scare even me…"
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_EnteredBunchOfContests {
	"I've entered a bunch of CONTESTS,
	so I'm seeing how things work.

	If you're in a COOLNESS CONTEST,
	cool moves go over as appeals.

	But smart moves and cute moves
	don't go over well, for instance."
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_ManWhoWonEarlierHadPokeblocks {
	"That young man who won earlier had
	a whole bunch of different {POKEBLOCK}S.

	Can you win if you had that many
	of those things?"
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_IsntThisPlaceHumongous {
	"Whoa, isn't this place humongous!

	The tension in the air… It's not
	like a CONTEST hall in the sticks."
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_GiveItBestSmartAppeal {
	"MC: Okay, SMART POKéMON and their
	TRAINERS, are you ready?!

	Give it your best showing!
	Let's appeal!"
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_AreYouEnjoyingThisContest {
	"JUDGE: Are you enjoying this CONTEST?

	Come back with three friends, and
	all of you may enter a CONTEST!"
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_EnteredWrongContest {
	"Ayayayay…
	I entered the wrong CONTEST.

	I entered this tough POKéMON in
	the SMARTNESS CONTEST…

	Come on, wow them with a smart-looking
	ROCK SMASH."
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_RaisedMonToBeSmart {
	"I've spent many a year, and all my
	wisdom besides, raising this POKéMON
	to be smart.

	It won't be easily bested by some
	young pup's POKéMON.

	My dear wife, are you seeing this?"
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_IfMonPullsSmartMoveNext {
	"There it is!

	If my POKéMON pulls a smart move next,
	the audience's excitement will peak!"
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_DontAppreciateCuteLeechLife {
	"Oh, dear, no!

	My darling ZUBAT's LEECH LIFE is so
	cute I kept using it over and over!

	But these mean people don't appreciate
	it at all!"
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_YoureBeautifulGrandpa {
	"Kiyaaah! You're beautiful, Grandpa!"
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_AllSeemToUseDifferentMoves {
	"Even when TRAINERS enter the same
	kind of POKéMON, they all seem to use
	different moves for appeals.

	It's just like the way people have
	different styles for battling."
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_PokemonSmarterThanTrainers {
	"I think the POKéMON look smarter
	than their TRAINERS. By a lot."
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_StillLoveSmartnessContests {
	"When all's said and done, I still love
	SMARTNESS CONTESTS.

	That intellectual green color…
	It's so… So… Cool."
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_AreYouEnteringBeautyContest {
	"MC: Are you entering the BEAUTY
	CONTEST, too? Good luck!"
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_EveryPokemonPristineBeauty {
	"JUDGE: Ah, every POKéMON here is
	a model of pristine beauty!

	Why, I almost forgot to score them!"
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_EyesWillBeGluedToMyBeauty {
	"A POKéMON this beautiful…
	There isn't another one like it.

	Everyone's eyes will be glued to
	my beauty."
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_OverdidGrooming {
	"Waaaah!

	I brushed and groomed my POKéMON
	carefully for this CONTEST…

	But I overdid it…
	My POKéMON's coat turned all scraggly…

	What should I do?"
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_JudgeWontSeeAuroraBeam {
	"This AURORA BEAM is so dazzling,
	the JUDGE won't be able to see it.

	Uh, wait a second…
	That'll be meaningless, then!"
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_PokemonLooksLikeYoungerMe {
	"This pretty POKéMON looks just like
	me when I was younger.

	Right when I said that, my husband
	spewed the coffee he was drinking.

	Did I say something funny?"
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_WinBeautyContestMakesMeHappy {
	"You know, if I win at a BEAUTY
	CONTEST, sure it makes me
	happy. More than usual, anyway."
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_GanderAtAllThosePrettyPokemon {
	"Wahahahah!

	Will you take a gander at all those
	pretty POKéMON!
	I just love this sort of glitz!"
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_CantWinOnBeautyAlone {
	"You can't always win on just beauty
	alone.

	You have to groom your POKéMON so
	it's nice and glossy like mine."
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_InTheMiddleOfContest {
	"MC: Uh-oh! Hello!
	We're in the middle of a CONTEST!

	Please enter at our registration
	counter and come out, okay?"
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_SuchCharmingCuteAppeals {
	"JUDGE: Oh, such charming and cute
	appeals!

	Oh, my goodness! What a perfectly
	adorable WATER SPORT appeal!"
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_MyAzurillWasDistracted {
	"Oh, no… My sweet AZURILL was
	distracted by another POKéMON."
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_NeverWonBattleButContest {
	"My POKéMON has never won in a battle,
	but put it in a CONTEST and look out!"
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_PetalDanceIsMarvel {
	"My POKéMON's PETAL DANCE is a marvel
	of elegance.

	I won't let anyone disturb its
	performance."
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_MyMonAppealSoMuchCuter {
	"Everyone's POKéMON are very cute.

	However, if my POKéMON were to make
	a cute appeal…

	I'm sure that it would be so much 
	cuter than the others."
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_MyChildIsInContest {
	"My child is in this CONTEST."
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_ComeOnDear {
	"Come on, dear. Go for it!
	Your POKéMON is the best!"
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_ThatGirlThereIsCutest {
	"I think that girl over there is
	the cutest of the lot.

	What's that? They're judging
	POKéMON by their looks?"
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_WantCuteMonOfMyOwn {
	"Ohh, seeing all these cute POKéMON,
	they make we want to get my own!

	I'm going to go catch some!"
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_BeautyContestStage {
	"BEAUTY CONTEST STAGE
	BE ALLURED BY BEAUTIFUL POKéMON!"
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_CuteContestStage {
	"CUTENESS CONTEST STAGE
	BE CHARMED BY CUTE POKéMON!"
}

text LilycoveCity_ContestHall_Text_SmartContestStage {
	"SMARTNESS CONTEST STAGE
	BE IMPRESSED BY SMART POKéMON!"
}
